(ooc: this is my first in character post.)
 Cut to a grassy plain. a small two man craft approaches. wall, a better word 
is plummets.
ghost: GAAAAAAAAAAAHHHH! WE'REGONNADIEOHSLAGWE'REGONNADIE!
goth: do you mind? we just flew through an asteroid belt,and now you're 
worried?
ghost begins to reply, but is cut off by an explosion, followed by the 
remains of the shuttle skidding about 150 feet.
ghost: worst. landing. ever.
goth: I tell you what, you radio for help, while i worry about how two cars 
are going to trave in the woods.
ghost: fine. ghost to any available parties, if anyone cares, 2 bots stranded 
in primus knows where, requesting assistance. over.

--part1_42.20d344fe.297c3c01_boundary
